{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_03_03",
  "title": "兵藤雫 3話 憧れの人と同じ舞台へ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――On the day of the live performance",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "リハーサル、凄く良かったじゃないか！\nあれから天動さんとどんな話をしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That rehearsal was amazing‚ wasn't it?\nWhat did you talk about with Tendo-san after that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "私は口下手だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm… not very good at speaking…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "昨今のアイドル業界の流行と傾向を分析して……\n二人の個性を最大限に生かすユニットを考えて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I analyzed the latest trends and tendencies in the idol industry…\nI thought of a unit that maximizes both of our unique points…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "思いついたアイデアやイメージを全て書き出して……\nそれらをレポートにまとめて瑠依さんに提出した……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wrote down every idea and image that came to mind…\nAnd compiled them into a report‚ which I then gave to Rui-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それは……天動さんも驚いていたんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder… if Tendo-san was surprised by that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依さんは感心して\nちゃんと全部に目を通してくれた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-san was impressed…\nShe thoroughly read through everything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "天動さんも真面目だからな……。確かに彼女なら\n自分にはない発想を見て素直に感心しそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tendou-san is very serious after all…\nShe would genuinely appreciate perspectives she hasn't considered.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依さんはいつも凜としてるから……\nたまには茶目っ気を出してみたらどうか、とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-san is always so poised…\nI suggested she might occasionally show her playful side…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "ファンと一緒になって楽しむ気持ちを\nもっと前面に出してみたらどうか、とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about putting more emphasis on the feeling\nof having fun together with the fans…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依さんの新しい一面や、私達ならこうした方が\n良くなると思うことを話し合ううちに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As we talked about Rui-san's new side\nand how we thought things would be better this way…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依さんと遠慮せず話せるようになった……\nこれも{user}さんのおかげ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I became able to speak with her without reservations…\nIt's all thanks to you‚ {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いいや、雫が頑張ったからだよ\n俺はちょっと背中を押しただけだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's because you worked hard.\nI just gave a little push.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "……私はアイドルが好き\n今でも応援してるアイドルは沢山いる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I love idols.\nI still support many idols to this day…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、お仕事で好きなアイドルと一緒になっても……\n本人には言わないようにしてた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But when I work with the idols I like‚\nI never tell them…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "今回も、ただの一ファンにならないように……\n練習中は気持ちを抑えなきゃって思ってた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time too‚ I tried not to become just another fan…\nI thought I had to keep my feelings in check during practice…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それも今日まで……今日は開き直って……\n瑠依さんへの憧れを解放しようと思ってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that's only up until today… Today‚ I'm going to let go…\nI'm thinking of unleashing my admiration for Rui-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "熱い思いを……瑠依さんと歌える喜びを……\nステージ上で爆発させる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My burning passion… and the joy of singing with Rui-san…\nI'll let it explode on stage…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "今までドルオタとして禁じてきたことを\nあえてやってみる訳か……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you're trying\nwhat you've been holding back as an idol otaku…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いいんじゃないか？　感情を爆発させることで\n今までの雫にはない新たな魅力が出せると思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds good‚ doesn't it? By letting your feelings burst‚\nI believe you can show a new charm that you haven't before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "うん……行ってくる……\n瑠依さんと一緒に歌える幸せを、思い切り表現してくる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… I'll be going now…\nI'll wholeheartedly express the joy of singing with Rui-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "（嬉しい……ずっと憧れていた瑠依さんと……）\n（一緒の舞台に立てるなんて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I'm so happy… To be on the same stage with Rui-san)\n(whom I've always admired as a idol…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "（サニピの時とは全然違う……けど、それが嫌じゃない）\n（いつもと違うことが楽しくて……ドキドキしてる……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(It's completely different with Sunny Peace… but I don't hate it.)\n(This different feeling… It's exciting and makes my heart race…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4466.66666660002,
          "startTime": 170.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "（凄い歓声……みんなも喜んでくれてる……）\n（私達二人を応援してくれてる……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Such loud cheers… Everyone seems to be enjoying it…)\n(They are all cheering for the two of us…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_03-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "（私がアイドルに憧れたみたいに……）\n（私も誰かの憧れになれてるのかな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Just like how I admired other idols…)\n(I wonder if I've become someone's idol too…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
