      "text": "だから、本当は瑠依さんとやりたいことがあったけど\nずっと我慢してた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were things I wanted to do with Rui-san‚\nBut I always held back…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
