      "text": "（根っこの部分は変わらないな……）\n（まぁ、そういうオタクな一面も雫の魅力だが）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But she hasn't changed at her core…)\n(Well‚ that otaku side of hers is part of Shizuku's charm.)",
        "id": ""
